data.description: Discover the epitome of comfortable family living in this charming home situated on a tranquil cul-de-sac street. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths within its 1675 sqft, this home is thoughtfully designed to meet the needs of everyone. The living room, adorned with a fireplace, creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, while a generously sized flex space exceeding 400 sqft offers versatility for use as a game room, theatre room, family room, or any personalized space to suit your lifestyle. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shopping, dining, and entertainment, ensuring that the best amenities are just moments away. With its close proximity to I-75, commuting is a breeze, making it even more convenient. Additionally, the direct access to Robins Air Force Base adds a unique advantage, making it an ideal location for military personnel or employees seeking both comfort and proximity. This home goes beyond being a mere residence; it provides a lifestyle tailored to everyone's needs. Whether you're unwinding by the fireplace or hosting gatherings in the expansive flex space, this home offers endless possibilities. Embrace the charm and convenience of this cul-de-sac property, perfectly blending comfort, style, and practicality. Contact me today to schedule a viewing and make this house your home--a place where lasting memories are waiting to be created. In order to make purchasing your new home a little easier, Seller will contribute up to $5000 for closing cost and/or points.
